      "content": "i've seen specialists. i've done the physical therapy, the pills, the everything. nothing works. it's just a slow decay. sometimes i look at it and i think, why am i even trying to stay here? it feels like im just clinging to a life that i dont even want anymore. it feels more like a burden than a life.",
