    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like something i can just \"find\" anymore. purpose doesn't really matter when every single movement is agony. it's like i'm just waiting for the clock to run out, but the clock is taking its sweet time. sometimes i think about how peaceful it would be to just... stop. to not have to wake up and feel this. is it wrong to want it to just be over? like, is there really any mercy in just continuing to suffer like this?",
